divs: sighting detailsjust watching sunset to the west. plano, texas. bright starlike object appeared out of nowhere. grabbed monoculures to look at it and saw two lights. thought to self it can't be star\planet. focused on with mono and took picture. that's when i saw the lights distinctively and to my surprise...a triangle shaped object. took two pics.no weird feelings or noise...too distant. however, 1hr or so before this...taking pic of sunset, noticed a black dot in pic. zoomed in and it appears to be a silver dome like disc.
Summary: Watching sunset; appeared 30 degs over horizon
